title: "OpenTelemetry-to-EEOAP Adapter: Transforming Agent Telemetry into Portable Operation Evidence"
abstract: "A package-local draft metadata record for a research software adapter that transforms controlled OpenTelemetry-style agent trace fixtures into EEOAP-compatible operation evidence statements, with committed fixtures, generated statements, adapter reports, scoped tests, and validation documentation. This file is a local draft and is not final public release metadata."
